Hey, did they find you?


1273
01:31:42.150 --> 01:31:45.180
-谁找我？ -马蒂，我想他们还在
-Who? -Marty. I don't think they've gone in yet.


1274
01:31:53.350 --> 01:31:54.680
马蒂
Marty.


1275
01:31:55.020 --> 01:31:58.220
