You're doing this now?


1310
01:33:36.710 --> 01:33:40.060
我说，我同意这么办，好吧？但有条件的
Look, I agreed to this, okay? But there's rules now.


1311
01:33:40.220 --> 01:33:43.090
你想要合同，就得签订一份保密协议
You want the contract, you sign a confidentiality agreement.


1312
01:33:43.250 --> 01:33:45.350
协议内容不能更改，同时具有追溯效力
It's gonna be bulletproof and retroactive.


1313
01:33:45.510 --> 01:33:47.250
因为马蒂这人很友善，不愿意说…
Because Marty's too nice to say it­


1314
01:33:47.410 --> 01:33:51.220
