1318
01:34:00.320 --> 01:34:02.920
-如果我错了，我道歉 -你他妈的完全错了
-If I'm wrong, I apologize -You're way the fuck wrong.


1319
01:34:03.090 --> 01:34:04.310
随你便好了
So there you go.


1320
01:34:04.490 --> 01:34:06.150
