You're just doing your job.


1331
01:35:33.590 --> 01:35:35.050
是啊
That's right.


1332
01:35:35.980 --> 01:35:37.720
保重，盖比
Take it easy, Gabe.


1333
01:35:38.720 --> 01:35:40.090
你也一样
Michael.


1334
01:35:51.820 --> 01:35:53.260
不跟
