不跟
Check.


1336
01:35:56.680 --> 01:35:59.420
-不跟 -半注，两百
-Check -Half the pot. Two hundred.


1337
01:35:59.580 --> 01:36:00.890
两百胜
Two hundred to go.


1338
01:36:38.220 --> 01:36:39.990
