So, what happened with the bar?


1339
01:36:40.150 --> 01:36:42.190
看来你经营的不善啊，哈？
You just had to be a rock star, huh?


1340
01:37:04.650 --> 01:37:07.420
你干什么？你才刚来
What are you doing? You just got here.


1341
01:37:07.580 --> 01:37:09.530
这哥们儿才玩了9手，这就走了
Guy plays nine hands, walks away.


1342
01:37:09.680 --> 01:37:13.850
我把你吓跑了？我干了什么？是我把你吓跑了吗？
I scare you away? What did I do? Did I scare you away?


1343
01:37:49.580 --> 01:37:50.650
快走
Get out.


1344
01:37:52.020 --> 01:37:54.150
快离开车子
Get out of the car now.


1345
01:37:55.880 --> 01:37:56.880
-沃尔特？ -迈克尔
-Walter? -Michael.


1346
01:37:57.050 --> 01:37:59.250
-迈克尔，谢天谢地，总算找到你 -嗯
-Michael. Thank God you're there -Yeah.


1347
01:38:03.650 --> 01:38:05.590
你还有8秒…
You have eight­


1348
01:38:06.480 --> 01:38:09.220
