Get out of the car.


1351
01:38:16.950 --> 01:38:19.980
-告诉他不要接任何电话了 -好的，你会去吧？
-Tell him to stay off the phone -All right. But you're on it?


1352
01:38:20.580 --> 01:38:22.030
